  "title": "Swing Showcase 2025",
  "description": "With flying flips, tapping feet, and fast dancing, Swing Showcase will inspire, thrill, and entertain. Take a journey through the dances of the swing-era, including Lindy Hop, Tap, Jazz, Blues, Balboa, and more! It’s a new show every year, produced by Sugar Swing Ballroom’s team, Mad Cat Swing.",
  "credits": "<strong>Director</strong>: Birkley Wisniewski<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Arta Seify, Birkley Wisniewski, Czarina Ramos, Dominic Wong, Janae Davies, Jasmine Farahbakhsh, Jason Thai, Katryna Drouin, Matt Lloyd, Paige Grant, Reinier Eubra, Rylee-Jane Chalifoux, Sarah Dickson, Tyrel Brochu<br/>",
  "website": "https://instagram.com/madcatswing",
  "plain_language": "Swing Showcase is a fun and exciting dance show. It is full of fast moves, fancy footwork, and energetic performances. You will see a variety of dances from the swing-era, like Lindy Hop, Tap, Jazz, Blues, and Balboa. The talented team Mad Cat Swing creates new routines every year, so the show is always different. It's a lively and entertaining experience for all ages!",
